{
  "stem": "22047.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in the ROTC, and we talked a lot about what was going on, and will the United States enter this war?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sure enough, in '41, we entered it whole hog.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] Do you remember Pearl Harbor?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember that day?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was, of course, in '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "December 7.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was still in Santa Barbara.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I recall hearing it on the radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, I remember the-- the newspaper people coming down our street, calling, extra, extra, Japanese attack Pearl Harbor!",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, we were on the radio then, listening to what was going on, and-- and oh my goodness.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then shortly thereafter, we had this Japanese submarine fired rounds-- came to the surface and fired rounds on the-- the beach in Santa Barbara and up near the oil fields in Goleta, that this Japanese sub had done that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, that involved us a lot, and we had the anti-aircraft guns going off, shooting at nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] There was a lot of hysteria in-- shortly after the Pearl Harbor episode.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I started realizing that young folks were-- were leaving and going to war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I began to wonder, well, I'm in a-- a military organization, the ROTC, in Santa Barbara High.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And am I going to be drafted when I become of age, or am I going to volunteer?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of folks were going into the military.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, well, maybe-- maybe that's not going to be too far off when I am.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I was certainly not against going in to-- to the war effort.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- as I said, he was involved with having gotten his commission.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was still involved in ROTC.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
